sem --
	Computer Science Seminar Announcements About sem English (USA) Announcements about upcoming seminars hosted by the Computer Science Department. To see the collection of prior postings to the list,
	      visit the sem
		  Archives .
	      ( The current archive is only available to the list
                members. ) Using sem To post a message to all the list members, send email to sem@cs.jhu.edu . You can subscribe to the list, or change your existing
	    subscription, in the sections below. Subscribing to sem Subscribe to sem by filling out the following
	      form.
	  You will be sent email requesting confirmation, to
            prevent others from gratuitously subscribing you. This is a hidden list, which means that the
            list of members is available only to the list administrator. Your email address: Your name (optional): You may enter a
	    privacy password below. This provides only mild security,
	    but should prevent others from messing with your
	    subscription. Do not use a valuable password as
	    it will occasionally be emailed back to you in cleartext. If you choose not to enter a password, one will be
            automatically generated for you, and it will be sent to
            you once you've confirmed your subscription.  You can
            always request a mail-back of your password when you edit
            your personal options. Pick a password: Reenter password to confirm: Which language do you prefer to display your messages? English (USA) Please answer the following question to prove that
                    you are not a bot: What is the three-letter abbreviation for Johns Hopkins University? sem Subscribers ( The subscribers list is only available to the list
            administrator. ) Enter your admin address and password to visit  the subscribers list: Admin address: Password: To unsubscribe from sem, get a password reminder,
        or change your subscription options enter your subscription
        email address: If you leave the field blank, you will be prompted for
        your email address sem list run by sem-owner at cs.jhu.edu sem administrative interface (requires authorization) Overview of all cs.jhu.edu mailing lists version 2.1.39
